title: &amp;quot;Jekyll 1.0.0 Released&amp;quot;
date: &amp;quot;2013-05-06 02:12:52 +0200&amp;quot;
author: parkr
version: 1.0.0
categories: [release]
---
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


